fields.description: Joint Complex is a super supplement with 10 active ingredients formulated for adults (aged 18 and over). Made in a unique forest fruit flavour using a natural sweetener, steviol glycosides, with ingredients including Peptan® Collagen Peptides (marine source), Hyaluronic Acid, Glucosamine, and MSM. It was created to deliver multiple benefits in one easy powdered sachet.

fields.name: BetterYou Magnesium Joint Body Spray
fields.description: BetterYou Magnesium Joint Body Spray is formulated to relieve muscle stiffness and improve joint flexibility. The formulation is absorbed immediately when sprayed onto skin, replenishing the body with this essential mineral.
fields.directions: Spray between five and ten sprays around the body and massage well into the skin to stimulate absorption. After a shower or bath is a great time to apply as the skin is warm and the pores are open which aids absorption.
fields.ingredients: Aqua (water), magnesium chloride, PEG-40 hydrogenated castor oil, acetyl glucosamine, propylene glycol, menthol, eucalyptus globulusleaf oil, limonene..

fields.name: Calcichew D3 Forte Tabs 500Mg 100s
fields.description: Calcichew D3 Forte chewable tablets contain two active ingredients, calcium carbonate, which is a calcium salt used mainly to supplement calcium in the diet, and colecalciferol, otherwise known as vitamin D3.
fields.directions: Adults and elderly: 2 chewable tablets per day, preferably one tablet morning and evening.The tablet may be chewed or sucked.
